@startuml Diagrama de Secuencia - Proceso de Venta

!define actor(x) actor "x"
!define participant(x) participant "x"
AZ
skinparam backgroundColor #FEFEFE
skinparam sequenceMessageAlign center

title Diagrama de Secuencia - Proceso de Venta (Flujo Principal)

actor "Cajero" as Cashier
participant "Frontend\n(Next.js)" as Frontend
participant "API\n(NestJS)" as API
participant "AuthGuard" as Auth
participant "Sales\nController" as SalesCtrl
participant "Sales\nService" as SalesSvc
participant "Prisma\nService" as Prisma
database "PostgreSQL" as DB

== Autenticacion ==

Cashier -> Frontend: 1. Iniciar sesion
Frontend -> API: POST /auth/login
API --> Frontend: JWT Token
Frontend --> Cashier: Dashboard cargado

== Crear Nueva Venta ==

Cashier -> Frontend: 2. Buscar producto
Frontend -> API: GET /products/search?q=laptop
API -> Auth: Validar JWT
Auth --> API: OK
API -> SalesCtrl:
SalesCtrl --> Prisma: findMany()
Prisma -> DB: SELECT * FROM products
DB --> Prisma: Resultados
Prisma --> SalesCtrl: Productos[]
SalesCtrl --> API: JSON Response
API --> Frontend: Lista de productos
Frontend --> Cashier: Mostrar resultados

== Agregar al Carrito ==

Cashier -> Frontend: 3. Agregar producto al carrito
Frontend -> Frontend: Actualizar estado local
Frontend --> Cashier: Carrito actualizado

Cashier -> Frontend: 4. Seleccionar cliente (opcional)
Frontend -> API: GET /customers
API -> Auth: Validar JWT
Auth --> API: OK
API --> Frontend: Lista de clientes
Frontend --> Cashier: Cliente seleccionado

Cashier -> Frontend: 5. Aplicar descuento
Frontend -> Frontend: Calcular totales
Frontend --> Cashier: Total actualizado

== Pausar Venta (Opcional) ==

opt Pausar Venta
    Cashier -> Frontend: 6. Pausar venta
    Frontend -> Frontend: Guardar en localStorage
    Frontend --> Cashier: Venta pausada

    Cashier -> Frontend: 6.1 Reanudar venta
    Frontend -> Frontend: Cargar de localStorage
    Frontend --> Cashier: Venta restaurada
end

== Procesar Pago ==

Cashier -> Frontend: 7. Procesar pago
Frontend -> Frontend: Calcular cambio
Frontend --> Cashier: Mostrar resumen

Cashier -> Frontend: 8. Confirmar venta
Frontend -> API: POST /sales
API -> Auth: Validar JWT
Auth --> API: OK

API -> SalesCtrl: createSale(dto)
SalesCtrl -> SalesSvc: createSale(dto, userId)

== Transaccion de Base de Datos ==

SalesSvc -> Prisma: $transaction(async tx => {)

SalesSvc -> Prisma: 8.1 Validar stock
Prisma -> DB: SELECT stock FROM products
DB --> Prisma: Stock actual
Prisma --> SalesSvc: Stock disponible

alt Stock Insuficiente
    SalesSvc --> SalesCtrl: Error: InsufficientStock
    SalesCtrl --> API: 409 Conflict
    API --> Frontend: Error message
    Frontend --> Cashier: Mostrar error
else Stock Suficiente
    SalesSvc -> Prisma: 8.2 Calcular totales
    SalesSvc -> Prisma: 8.3 Crear venta
    Prisma -> DB: INSERT INTO sales
    DB --> Prisma: Venta creada

    SalesSvc -> Prisma: 8.4 Crear items de venta
    Prisma -> DB: INSERT INTO sale_items
    DB --> Prisma: Items creados

    SalesSvc -> Prisma: 8.5 Registrar pagos
    Prisma -> DB: INSERT INTO payments
    DB --> Prisma: Pagos registrados

    SalesSvc -> Prisma: 8.6 Actualizar stock
    Prisma -> DB: UPDATE products SET stock = stock - qty
    DB --> Prisma: Stock actualizado

    SalesSvc -> Prisma: 8.7 Registrar movimiento
    Prisma -> DB: INSERT INTO inventory_movements
    DB --> Prisma: Movimiento registrado

    Prisma --> SalesSvc: Transaccion completada
end

SalesSvc --> SalesCtrl: Sale object
SalesCtrl --> API: 201 Created
API --> Frontend: Venta creada + datos

== Generar Recibo ==

Frontend -> API: POST /sales/{id}/receipt
API -> SalesCtrl: generateInvoice(id)
SalesCtrl -> SalesSvc:
SalesSvc -> Prisma: findUnique()
Prisma -> DB: SELECT * FROM sales WHERE id = ?
DB --> Prisma: Datos completos
Prisma --> SalesSvc: Venta con items

SalesSvc --> SalesCtrl: PDF Buffer/URL
SalesCtrl --> API:
API --> Frontend: URL de recibo PDF

Frontend --> Cashier: 9. Venta completada!
Frontend --> Cashier: Descargar/Imprimir recibo

== Cancelar Venta (Alternativa) ==

opt Cancelar Venta (Solo Admin)
    Cashier -> Frontend: Cancelar venta
    Frontend -> API: PUT /sales/{id}/status
    API -> Auth: Validar JWT + Rol ADMIN
    Auth --> API: OK

    API -> SalesCtrl: cancelSale(id)
    SalesCtrl -> SalesSvc:
    SalesSvc -> Prisma: $transaction()

    SalesSvc -> Prisma: Revertir stock
    Prisma -> DB: UPDATE products SET stock = stock + qty
    DB --> Prisma: OK

    SalesSvc -> Prisma: Actualizar estado
    Prisma -> DB: UPDATE sales SET status = 'CANCELLED'
    DB --> Prisma: OK

    SalesSvc -> Prisma: Registrar cancelacion
    Prisma -> DB: INSERT INTO inventory_movements
    DB --> Prisma: OK

    Prisma --> SalesSvc: Transaccion completada
    SalesSvc --> SalesCtrl:
    SalesCtrl --> API: 200 OK
    API --> Frontend: Venta cancelada
    Frontend --> Cashier: Confirmacion
end

@enduml
